      "settings": {
        "checksum": "4d0229436f22331b38906db58390086698045eed34f3b489d8c8f7bdd43bb3f0_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg81WwevIKk_childItem_0": "<p>100% Made In Italy</p>",
        "gg81WwevIKk_childItem_1": "<p>Dermatologically Tested</p>",
        "gg81WwevIKk_childItem_2": "<p>No More Bags and Dark Circles.</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_0": "<p>What happened to Omnis? Why is it now SerlinoLab?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_1": "<p>Who is it for?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_2": "<p>How long does it last?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_3": "<p>How to use it?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_4": "<p>How long does it take to see results?</p>",
        "ggCdVdus-lO_text": "<p>If the product doesn't meet your expectations, you have up to 60 days to request a complete refund, without any complications.</p>",
        "ggFipoBsWwP_text": "<p><strong>Morning and evening, </strong>after cleaning and drying your face, press the button located on the top of the bottle once and distribute the cream around the eye contour.<br><br>Using the metal ball massager, make<strong> circular movements until completely absorbed.</strong></p>",
        "ggKZrkCgfQz_text": "<p>The SerlinoLab eye contour is the ideal solution for men who want to:</p><ul><li><strong>Prevent</strong> and <strong>reduce </strong>bags under the eyes</li><li><strong>Eliminate </strong>unsightly dark circles</li><li><strong>Appear </strong>more rested and in shape</li></ul>",
        "ggNgskm7d42_text": "<p>Based on the experiences of <strong>multiple customers,</strong> you can already see the first results after the <strong>first days of use.</strong><br><br>Like any investment though, give this product the benefit of time.<br><br>The best results are achieved with continued use, twice a day, for 8-12 weeks.</p>",
        "ggR8kqovO2L_text": "<p>1 eye contour lasts <strong>1 month</strong> when used twice a day, morning and evening.</p>",
        "ggSzrYgvgcA_text": "<p><strong>4.6 Excellent</strong> | 3,439+ reviews</p>",
        "ggVLmbUDTCI_text": "<p>\"I've been using it for 2 weeks, a colleague asked me if I went on vacation... finally goodbye bags and dark circles!!\"</p>",
        "ggbsEHDd1cH_label": "Add to Cart",
        "ggbsEHDd1cH_outOfStockLabel": "Out of stock",
        "ggbsEHDd1cH_unavailableLabel": "Unavailable",
        "ggbsEHDd1cH_variantSelectionRequiredMessage": "Please select a variant to add product to cart",
        "ggd3njxJyN7_text": "60-day Guarantee",
        "gggTQ3oQA5C_text": "New: <strong>Omnis</strong> has become <strong>SerlinoLab</strong>.<br>Same formula, new look",
        "ggjU9YlrJZq_text": "Delivery in 24-48 hours",
        "ggtTyjg3ZOP_text": "<p>We updated our name and packaging to better reflect the <strong>true Italian identity</strong> of our brand.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>The formulas? Exactly the same.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Same ingredients, same quality, same lab on the Amalfi Coast.</p><p><strong>Just a new look.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We hope you like it as much as we do!</p>",
        "ggviiph8ERl_text": "<p>Eye Cream • 15ml</p>",
        "section_preload": "true"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-604270698126443179"
    },
