    "gp_section_604270984798667439": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "3f1fb4931cb8d4dd77f372baddb1dce10a3ba4b6cba04aee3eaf7eea06a75a93_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggcgBQgtPq9_text": "Dermatologically <br><span style=\"color:#17162E;\">Tested in Italy 🇮🇹</span>",
        "ggn_plRY9PV_text": "<p>All SerlinoLab creams are <strong>Made in Italy,</strong> produced by a<strong> small family owned</strong> <strong>lab with 38 years of experience.</strong></p><p> </p><p>❌ You won’t find: silicones, parabens, alcohol, synthetic fragrances. And of course, we do NOT test on animals!</p>",
        "ggqxwscrgeF_text": "<span style=\"color:#17162E;\">Dermatologically Tested in Italy 🇮🇹</span>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-604270984798667439"
    },
    "gp_section_604271087928214497": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "6b4cbe04c28ff76c490845b8f7a2d3e218e52d985c2ae0e3b5530adf300a142c_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg2geC5QU78_text": "<p>More compact and toned skin in <strong>2 weeks</strong></p>",
        "ggFuswS2tET_text": "<span style=\"color:#17162E;\"><strong>From the First Application, Softer and More Elastic Skin</strong></span>",
        "ggHAddg1wYA_text": "<p>Visible <strong>wrinkle reduction*</strong></p>",
        "ggIXwq5Z3qz_text": "<p>Confirms rapid absorption <strong>without greasy effect</strong></p>",
        "ggKZYDBnoUY_text": "<p>*Tests conducted on 124 men for 60 days</p>",
        "ggbtmoS_6pe_text": "From the First Application,<br><span style=\"color:#17162E;\">Softer and More Elastic Skin</span>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-604271087928214497"
    },
    "gp_section_604271088146317995": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "012d32d0824e490fba6f87438fa839039dc2257c1d8254a7a5c44754ca92b061_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg499vyqQbK_label": "<p>GRAPE EXTRACT</p>",
        "gg9vSbtTCtd_text": "<p>A Made in Italy formula that tackles the problem at its root</p>",
        "ggHTNcdybNs_label": "<p>SODIUM HYALURONATE</p>",
        "ggIi2WelVfh_text": "<p>A peptide that relaxes the muscles around the eyes, naturally softening expression lines.</p><p> </p><p><strong>BENEFITS:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Reduces crow's feet</li>\n<li>Smooths fine lines</li>\n<li>Visibly smoother skin</li>\n</ul>",
        "ggOCBvCsSRm_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">AQUA [WATER], ALOE BARBADENSIS LEAF JUICE, GLYCERIN, SODIUM POLYACRYLATE, NIACINAMIDE, ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN OIL, PHENOXYETHANOL, CAFFEINE, TOCOPHERYL ACETATE, HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED OIL, UREA, TREHALOSE, HYDROLYZED RICE PROTEIN, VITIS VINIFERA (GRAPE) JUICE, ETHYLHEXYLGLYCERIN, CITRUS AURANTIUM BERGAMIA (BERGAMOT) FRUIT OIL, SODIUM CARBOXYMETHYL BETAGLUCAN, LINALYL ACETATE, LINALOOL, LIMONENE, CITRIC ACID, LAVANDULA ANGUSTIFOLIA (LAVENDER) OIL, ALTHAEA OFFICINALIS ROOT EXTRACT, CALENDULA OFFICINALIS FLOWER EXTRACT, MALVA SYLVESTRIS (MALLOW) LEAF EXTRACT, CAPRYLYL GLYCOL, HYDROXYETHYLCELLULOSE, POTASSIUM SORBATE, SODIUM BENZOATE, SODIUM HYALURONATE, BENZYL ALCOHOL, PINENE, ACETUM, BETA-CARYOPHYLLENE, TERPINEOL, ACETYL HEXAPEPTIDE-8, ASCORBIC ACID, PENTAPEPTIDE-18</span></p>",
        "ggQcytW0Qx-_text": "<p>A low molecular weight form that penetrates deeper than regular hyaluronic acid.</p><p> </p><p><strong>BENEFITS:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Penetrates deeply</li>\n<li>Fills fine lines from within</li>\n<li>Plumper, more hydrated skin</li>\n</ul>",
        "ggb3Bc9Bfkr_text": "<p>Rich in polyphenols and vitamin C, strengthens capillaries and brightens dark circles.</p><p> </p><p><strong>BENEFITS:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Brightens dark circles</li>\n<li>Strengthens fragile capillaries</li>\n<li>Illuminates the eye area</li>\n</ul>",
        "ggcjHoeC6qt_text": "<span style=\"color:#17162E;\">Triple Action Against Bags, Dark Circles, and Wrinkles</span>",
        "ggm1iHtTUig_label": "<p>ACETYL HEXAPEPTIDE-8</p>",
        "ggq53uKM9AC_childItem_0": "<p>Full Ingredient List</p>",
        "ggx4r9v03KH_label": "<p>CAFFEINE</p>",
        "ggyEadoL8pn_text": "<p>Stimulates microcirculation and constricts blood vessels, reducing puffiness under the eyes.</p><p> </p><p><strong>BENEFITS:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Reduces puffiness fast</li>\n<li>Drains excess fluids</li>\n<li>Fresher, more rested look</li>\n</ul>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-604271088146317995"
    },
    "gp_section_604271108329308843": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "11e6123f2596004c5d21f8f28bc44ef30951c210480970eddb8200fa611f7f27_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg4E8myjkrY_text": "<p><strong>NO </strong>at the moment the <strong>SerlinoLab Eye Contour is only available on our website.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We have chosen to sell only online to <strong>maintain competitive prices</strong> by avoiding intermediaries and <strong>offer </strong>a shopping experience with <strong>personalized advice</strong> for each customer on WhatsApp, which would not be possible in physical stores.</p>",
        "gg7xPh9jIxj_text": "<p>If after 60 days you haven't seen the results you expected, you can write to us and you will be <strong>refunded 100%</strong>... yes we are that confident in our products!</p>",
        "ggLeXHdEWgH_text": "<p>The SerlinoLab eye contour is made with the highest quality ingredients. Suitable for every skin type, even the most sensitive ones. Particularly recommended for mature skin.</p>",
        "ggR0ua9eMRk_text": "<p>Like any investment, give this product the benefit of time. The best results are achieved with continued use, twice a day, for 8-12 weeks.</p>",
        "ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_0": "<p>What happened to Omnis? Why is it now SerlinoLab?</p>",
        "ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_1": "<p>Can it be found in stores/pharmacies?</p>",
        "ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_2": "<p>How long does it take to see results?</p>",
        "ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_3": "<p>How to use it?</p>",
        "ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_4": "<p>How does the 60-day guarantee work?</p>",
        "ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_5": "<p>How long does this cream last?</p>",
        "ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_6": "<p>Is it suitable for sensitive skin?</p>",
        "ggRtYYRj3Jl_childItem_7": "<p>What ingredients are in the eye contour?</p>",
        "ggUqzxYOX9P_text": "<p>With daily use morning and evening, the cream will last you for 1 month.</p>",
        "ggWddcJAESW_text": "<span style=\"color:#17162E;\">Do You Still Have Any Doubts?</span>",
        "ggeyv3nvcwe_text": "<p>We updated our name and packaging to better reflect the true Italian identity of our brand.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The formulas? Exactly the same.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Same ingredients, same quality, same lab on the Amalfi Coast.</p><p>Just a new look.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We hope you like it as much as we do</p>",
        "ggnj2HWJKbX_text": "<p>The main ingredients are hyaluronic acid, caffeine and acetyl hexapeptide-8.<br><br>You can find the complete list here:<br><br>INCI<br><br>Aqua, aloe barbadensis leaf juice, glycerin, sodium polyacrylate, niacinamide, oryza sativa bran oil, phenoxyethanol, caffeine, tocopheryl acetate, helianthus annuus seed oil, urea, trehalose, hydrolyzed rice protein, ethylhexylglycerin, citrus aurantium bergamia fruit oil, sodium carboxymethyl betaglucan, lavandula angustifolia oil, linalool, limonene, sodium benzoate, linalyl acetate, althaea officinalis root extract, calendula officinalis flower extract, malva sylvestris leaf extract, hydroxyethylcellulose, potassium sorbate, sodium hyaluronate, benzyl alcohol, caprylyl glycol, pinene, acetyl hexapeptide-8, ascorbic acid, citric acid, pentapeptide-18.</p>",
        "ggwnWc2z9ft_text": "<p><strong>Morning and evening,</strong> after cleaning and drying your face, press the button located on the top of the bottle once and distribute the cream around the eye contour.<br><br>Using the metal ball massager, <strong>make circular movements until completely absorbed.</strong><br><br>A single dose is enough for both eyes.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-604271108329308843"
    },
